        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p>At Greenlight Loans, customer service, trust and confidence is a high priority. That's why we welcome this opportunity to describe our privacy policies, the steps we take to protect and maintain your information and to let you know how you can choose how your customer information may be shared.</p>
